T02TD2274E:124a-1: dva da sha au pa de sha g'a th'a /
T02TD2274E:124a-3: man ngag gi tshigs su bcad pa bcu gnyis pa /
T02TD2274E:124a-4: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2274E:124b-0: byang chub sems ni @124b zhi ba ste //
T02TD2274E:124b-1: de la gnas pa gang yin pa //
T02TD2274E:124b-2: nam mkha' bzhin du zhi bar 'gyur //
T02TD2274E:124b-3: lus ngag yid las byung ba yi //
T02TD2274E:124b-4: de la cung zad 'gyur ba med //
T02TD2274E:124b-5: yang dag ye shes las 'das pa //
T02TD2274E:124b-6: rnam par mi rtog zhi bar 'gyur //
T02TD2274E:124b-7: rtog pa zhi ba sangs rgyas nyid //
T02TD2274E:124b-8: de nyid rnam pa mkhyen nyid do //
T02TD2274E:124b-9: dngos po dngos po mthong nas ni //
T02TD2274E:124b-10: de ltar rnam rtog gang byung ba //
T02TD2274E:124b-11: de ni rtog med ye shes yin //
T02TD2274E:124b-13: dngos po kun gyi rang bzhin no //
T02TD2274E:124b-14: thams cad du ni so sor gnas //
T02TD2274E:124b-15: de dgal ni khyad par du //
T02TD2274E:124b-16: nga rgyal med cing rmongs pa med //
T02TD2274E:124b-17: de phyogs phyogs gcig dngos po la //
T02TD2274E:124b-18: bdag tu 'dzin pa ji ltar yin //
T02TD2274E:124b-19: dud 'gro la sogs rang bzhin no //
T02TD2274E:124b-20: phyogs gcig tsam las gang byung ba //
T02TD2274E:124b-21: de yi ngo bor bshad par bya //
T02TD2274E:124b-22: yang dag sems kyis gzung bar byos //
T02TD2274E:124b-23: stag ni phug na gnas pa dang //
T02TD2274E:124b-24: sbal pa stong pa chen po dang //
T02TD2274E:124b-25: byi la ba spu ldang ba dang //
T02TD2274E:124b-26: ba lang la sogs lus po sprug / sbrul la bza' ba med pa dang //
T02TD2274E:124b-27: bya rnams mkha' la 'gro ba dang //
T02TD2274E:124b-29: rnga mos sbrul rnams 'gugs pa dang //
T02TD2274E:124b-30: rma bya skom las rgyal ba dang //
T02TD2274E:124b-31: bung bas dug rnams zos pa dang //
T02TD2274E:124b-32: chu byas dbang po bsdams ba dang //
T02TD2274E:124b-33: seng ge 'jigs pa med pa dang //
T02TD2274E:124b-34: 'ug pas mtshan mo mthong ba dang //
T02TD2274E:124b-35: bya rgod rin chen rtogs pa dang //
T02TD2274E:124b-36: sbrul gyi dug ni byed pa dang //
T02TD2274E:124b-37: rma byas dug rnams za ba dang ;
T02TD2274E:124b-38: / dur pas ma 'ongs shes pa dang //
T02TD2274E:124b-39: ni tsho tshig la mkhas pa dang //
T02TD2274E:124b-40: sbrang bus rjes rnams sdud pa dang //
T02TD2274E:124b-43: bung ba'i skad ni shin du snyan //
T02TD2274E:124b-44: chu skyar mchil mas sems can 'dzin //
T02TD2274E:124b-45: sbrul gyi mig gis thos pa dang //
T02TD2274E:124b-46: ri dgas las ni gla rtsi 'byung //
T02TD2274E:124b-47: gu na sa ni mig gis snom //
T02TD2274E:124b-48: chu yi nang na gnas pa'i nya //
T02TD2274E:124b-49: srog dang rtsol bas 'gog par byed //
T02TD2274E:124b-50: tshul ngan bzlas pa bram ze yis //
T02TD2274E:124b-51: ye shes mchog tu thal bar 'gyur //
T02TD2274E:125a-2: snga ma'i bag chags las byung ba'i //
T02TD2274E:125a-4: de dag 'jig rten ye shes can //
T02TD2274E:125a-5: dka' thub ma yin grol ba min //
T02TD2274E:125a-6: snga ma'i bag chags las byung ba'i //
T02TD2274E:125a-7: de dag so sor gnas pa yin //
T02TD2274E:125a-8: de tsam ye shes yin na ni //
T02TD2274E:125a-10: de ltar shes te zhen spangs nas //
T02TD2274E:125a-11: yang dag ye shes spyad par bya //
T02TD2274E:125a-12: gang gis byang chub dam pa dag / dngos grub dam pa 'byung bar 'gyur //
T02TD2274E:125a-13: man ngag gi tshigs su bcad pa bcu gnyis pa bram ze chen pos ra ha'i zhal nas gsungs pa rdzogs so//
